Package: dqtesting
Type: Package
Title: Easy to use tools for data quality testing
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Emanuel Sommer <emanuel_sommer@gmx.de>
Maintainer: Emanuel Sommer <emanuel_sommer@gmx.de>
Description: The goal of the package is to provide an easy toolset for data quality testing. The main function perform_dqtest returns a list containing various results from an univariate DQ test. Moreover functions are provided that allow a very easy interface to the Local Outlier Factor Algorithm for multivariate outlier detection (therefore automated hyperparameter tuning). 
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
